###############################################################################
# SPRINT PROMPTS (lead .ptl → then task .pd in dispatch order)
###############################################################################
S34: sprints/34/S34.ptl — Vue Component Refactoring (P0). Tasks: T1 audit, T2 LoginView, T3 SouthernLights, T4/T5 remaining.
S35: sprints/35/S35.ptl — Graphics Fallback WGPU→WebGL→HTML (P1). Tasks: T1 design, T2 capability detector, T3 integration.
S36: sprints/36/S36.ptl — Slint/HTML switch, HTML default (P2). Tasks: T1 switch design, T2 implementation, T3 verify default.
S37: sprints/37/S37.ptl — Architecture consolidation, PWA fallbacks, docs (P3). Tasks: T1 platform audit, T2 abstraction, T3 PWA, T4 docs.
S38: sprints/38/S38.ptl — Async Reports + 2FA (P1, dep S37). Backlog H-002, H-003, F-004.
S39: sprints/39/S39.ptl — Feature Pack (P2, dep S38). F-001, F-002, F-005, M-007, F-007.
S40: sprints/40/S40.ptl — Tech Debt Cleanup (P3, dep S39). wgpu/rust update, M-002.
S20: sprints/20/S20.ptl — Universal UI Template (optional).
S21: sprints/21/S21.ptl — Rebrand Login WOW (optional).
S27: sprints/27/S27.ptl — Release Go-Live (CI/CD, store assets, runbook).

###############################################################################
# HOW TO RUN
###############################################################################
1. Open this file (EPIC1-TO-DO.pi) for overview.
2. Pick sprint (start with S34). Open sprints/NN/S34.ptl (or S35.ptl, etc.).
3. Run phases in order: plan → design → develop → verify → close.
4. For each phase, run tasks listed in dispatch (open S34-T1-*.pd, S34-T2-*.pd, etc.).
5. Verify: pnpm run test, pnpm run build (from navitrack-app).

###############################################################################
# SUCCESS
###############################################################################
Epic 1 complete when: refactoring S34–S37 done; backlog S38–S40 done or scoped; optional S20/S21 and S27 as needed. All builds and tests pass.
